-06-30\"/>\n|Active<ref name=\"Tate_2017-06-30\"/>\n|-\n|546<ref name=\"oni_2015_PLAN_ID_Guide\"/><ref name=\"Yeo_2014-12-08\"/>\n|\u76d0\u57ce/ ''Yancheng''<ref name=\"oni_2015_PLAN_ID_Guide\"/><ref name=\"Yeo_2014-12-08\"/>\n|\n|\n|\n|North Sea Fleet<ref name=\"Yeo_2014-12-08\"/>\n|Active<ref name=\"Tate_2015-05-14\">{{cite web |url=http://www.janes.com/article/51461/us-announces-then-clarifies-b-1-deployment-to-australia-ramps-up-south-china-sea-rhetoric |title=US announces, then 'clarifies' B-1 deployment to Australia, ramps up South China Sea rhetoric |last1=Hardy |first1=James |date=14 May 2015 |website=IHS Jane's 360 |access-date=5 August 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150718121415/http://www.janes.com/article/51461/us-announces-then-clarifies-b-1-deployment-to-australia-ramps-up-south-china-sea-rhetoric |archive-date=18 July 2015 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n|547<ref name=\"oni_2015_PLAN_ID_Guide\"/>\n|\u4e34\u6c82/ ''Linyi''<ref name=\"oni_2015_PLAN_ID_Guide\"/>\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|Active<ref name=\"Weening_2014-12-02\">{{cite web |url=http://www.janes.com/article/46631/china-sends-19th-naval-escort-piracy-task-force-to-somalia |title=China sends 19th naval escort piracy task force to Somalia |last1=Weening |first1=Cornelius |date=2 December 2014 |website=IHS Jane's 360 |access-date=5 August 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926154538/http://www.janes.com/article/46631/china-sends-19th-naval-escort-piracy-task-force-to-somalia |archive-date=26 September 2015 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n|548<ref name=\"oni_2015_PLAN_ID_Guide\"/>\n|\u76ca\u9633/ ''Yiyang''<ref name=\"oni_2015_PLAN_ID_Guide\"/>\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|Active\n|-\n|549<ref name=\"oni_2015_PLAN_ID_Guide\"/><ref name=\"Rahmat_2014-09-21\">{{cite web |url=http://www.janes.com/article/43499/china-sends-destroyer-frigate-to-iran-in-sign-of-growing-naval-ties |title=China sends destroyer, frigate to Iran in sign of growing naval ties |last1=Rahmat |first