ese]] \n**Proposed state:[[Bali|Balinese Republic]]<ref>http://www.muslimedianews.com/2014/08/tahun-2015-indonesia-pecah-ini-petanya.html</ref><ref>https://www.facebook.com/Gerakan-Bali-Merdeka-173532122764277/</ref>\n**Advocacy group: [[Baduy Society]], [[Bali Fourm]], [[Bali Freedom Movement]]\n**Political party: [[Dharma Awakening Party]]\n\n[[File:Flag of North Sumatra.svg|22px|border]] [[North Sumatra|Batakia]]\n*Ethnic group: [[Bataks]]\n**Proposed state:[[North Sumatra|Batakia]]<ref>http://parlinpakpahan.blogspot.com.es/2010/03/lmmt-solusi-politik-untuk-pemekaran.html</ref>\n**Political party: [[Batak Nation Party]]\n**Advocacy group: [[Bangso Batak]], [[O Tano Batak]], [[Batak Heritage Society]], [[Batak Worldwide]], [[Arys Christian Sinambela]], [[Batak Nauli]], [[Free Batak Homeland]], [[Free North Sumatra]]\n\n[[Kalimantan]]\n* Proposed state: [[File:Flag of Kalimantan Borneo.png|22x20px|border]] [[Kalimantan Borneo]], unification with {{flag|Malaysia}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tribunnews.com/nasional/2011/08/04/perhatian-buruk-warga-perbatasan-ancam-kibarkan-bendera-malaysia |title=Perhatian Buruk! Warga Perbatasan Ancam Kibarkan Bendera Malaysia |publisher=Tribun News |date=4 August 2011 |accessdate=4 July 2014 |language=Indonesian |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714152715/http://www.tribunnews.com/nasional/2011/08/04/perhatian-buruk-warga-perbatasan-ancam-kibarkan-bendera-malaysia |archive-date=14 July 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.itoday.co.id/politik/duh-wni-di-perbatasan-ancam-gabung-ke-malaysia?q=/politik/7351-duh-wni-di-perbatasan-ancam-gabung-ke-malaysia |title=Duh, WNI di Perbatasan Ancam Gabung ke Malaysia |publisher=I Today |date=1 May 2012 |accessdate=4 July 2014 |language=Indonesian |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714151218/http://www.itoday.co.id/politik/duh-wni-di-perbatasan-ancam-gabung-ke-malaysia?q=%2Fpolitik%2F7351-duh-wni-di-perbatasan-ancam-gabung-ke-malaysia |archive-d