au]]\n** Advocacy group: Gerakan Riau Merdeka<ref>{{cite journal |url=https://www.academia.edu/6935750 |title=Tabrani Rab dan Gerakan Riau Merdeka |first=Ronny |last=Basista |journal=\u2014 |access-date=13 December 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217191755/http://www.academia.edu/6935750/Tabrani_Rab_dan_Gerakan_Riau_Merdeka |archive-date=17 February 2017 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n[[File:Coat of Arms, Tana Toraga Regency.png|22px|border]] [[Tana Toraja Regency|Tana Toraja]]\n*Ethnic group: [[Toraja people|Torajan]]\n**Proposed state:Tana Toraja<ref>https://www.karebatoraja.com/video-memaknai-kemerdekaan-di-bagian-terluar-tana-toraja/</ref>\n**Advocacy group: Bonggakaradeng\n\n== Iran ==\n{{Main|Secession in Iran}}\n\n[[Azerbaijan (Iran)]]\n* Ethnic group: [[Azerbaijan people|Azeri]]\n** Proposed state: Merge with {{flag|Republic of Azerbaijan}}\n** Political party: CAMAH ([[Southern Azerbaijan National Awakening Movement|South Azerbaijan National Liberation Movement]])<ref>{{cite web |url=http://southazerbaijan.info/en/nizam.php |title=Archived copy |access-date=4 January 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130221090146/http://southazerbaijan.info/en/nizam.php# |archive-date=21 February 2013 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n\n[[Kh\u016bzest\u0101n Province|Kh\u016bzest\u0101n]]\n* Ethnic group: [[Arabs|Arab]]\n** Proposed state: [[Al-Ahwaz|Islamic Republic of Al-Ahwaz]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.al-ahwaz.com/english/2009/index.php?page=news&a_p_no=1&w_p_no=1&ar_p_no=23-1-2008-1 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=28 July 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100812065826/http://www.al-ahwaz.com/english/2009/index.php?page=news&a_p_no=1&w_p_no=1&ar_p_no=23-1-2008-1 |archivedate=12 August 2010 }} National Libration{{sic}} Movement of Ahwaz</ref> [[File:Flag of Arabistan.svg|22px|border]]\n** Militant organisations: [[Al-Ahwaz Arab People's Democratic Popular Front]], [[Ahwaz Arab Renaissance Party]], [