ital Region]]\n* Proposed autonomous area: [[Metro Manila]] Autonomous Region<ref>{{cite news |title=QC mayor Bautista seeks 'independent Metro Manila state' |url=https://www.rappler.com/nation/179009-quezon-city-mayor-herbert-bautista-independent-metro-manila-state |accessdate=31 August 2017 |work=Rappler |date=17 August 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170831083111/https://www.rappler.com/nation/179009-quezon-city-mayor-herbert-bautista-independent-metro-manila-state |archive-date=31 August 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n[[Federal Republic of Mindanao]]\n*[[Mindanao]], [[Palawan (island)|Palawan]] and [[Sulu Archipelago|Sulu]]\n\n== Russia ==\n{{More citations needed section|small=y|date=January 2020}}\n{{Main|Secession in Russia}}\n{{See also|List of active separatist movements in Europe#Russia|Asian Russia|Indigenous peoples of Siberia}}\n\n===Summary===\nThis table shows only the list of movements. The source of each movement is cited in its own section. The population of each area is provided for information only.\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%\"\n|-\n!width=75|Number\n!width=250|Land\n!width=125|Capital\n!width=100|Area\n!width=100|Population\n!width=125|Ethnic\n!width=300|Main Political Party\n|-\n| colspan=\"7\" bgcolor=\"#9acdff\" align=\"center\" |'''All of [[Asian Russia]]'''\n|-\n| align=center|1 || '''[[File:Siberian flag.svg|23px|border]] [[Siberian Republic]]''' || '''[[Novosibirsk]]''' || align=center|13,100,000  || align=center|40,000,000 || [[Siberia|Sibiryak people]] || [[Siberian regionalism]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"7\" bgcolor=\"#9acdff\" align=\"center\" |'''[[Far Eastern Federal District]] of [[Asian Russia]]'''\n|-\n| align=center|2 || '''[[File:Flag of Sakha.svg|23px|border]] [[Sakha Republic]]''' || '''[[Yakutsk]]''' || align=center|3,083,523 || align=center|1,000,000 || [[Yakut people|Yakuts]] || Sakha-Amuk\n|-\n| align=center|3 || '''[[File:Flag of the Far Eastern Republic.svg|23px|border]] [[Far Eastern Republic