928\n| <ref name=\"Neuenschwander\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Oskee Wow-Wow]]\n| {{sortname|Harold Vater|Hill|nolink=1}} '11\n| {{sortname|Howard Ruggles|Green|nolink=1}} '12\n| 1910\n| <ref name=\"Illinois Song Archives\"/><ref name=\"University of Illinois Songbook\"/><ref name=\"Illini Songbook\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Pride of the Illini\n| {{sortname|Karl Lawrence|King|Karl King}}\n| {{sortname|Raymond Francis|Dvorak|nolink=1}} '22 '26\n| 1928\n| <ref name=\"Neuenschwander\"/>\n|}\n\n==Performed in the past==\nThe following songs used to see regular performance through the university band or orchestra, campus glee clubs, or other means. As of recent history, they are no longer performed regularly.\n\n[[File:\"Fight Illini\" Cover.jpg|thumb|Front cover of \"Fight Illini.\"]]\n[[File:\"Have Courage, Illinois\".jpg|thumb|Front cover of \"Have Courage, Illinois.\"]]\n[[File:\"University of Illinois March\" Cover.jpg|thumb|Front cover of \"University of Illinois March.\"]]\n[[File:\"Where the Boneyard Flows\" Cover.jpg|thumb|Front cover of \"Where the Boneyard Flows.\"]]\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Title\n! Composer\n! Lyricist\n! Written\n! {{abbr|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Academic Professional\n|colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"|{{sortname|Lloyd|Morey}} '11\n| 1955\n| <ref name=\"Illinois Song Archives\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Alma Mater\n| {{sortname|Arthur Everett|Holch, Sr.|nolink=1}} '13\n| {{sortname|Ralph Edgar|Holch|nolink=1}} '10\n| 1912\n| <ref name=\"Illinois Song Archives\"/><ref name=\"University of Illinois Songbook\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Back Illinois\n|colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"|{{sortname|Vernon Thompson|Stevens|nolink=1}} '15 '17\n| 1914\n| <ref name=\"Illinois Song Archives\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Come, All Ye Loyal Rooters!<br/>(Illinois Field Song)\n|colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"|{{sortname|Edward George|Oldefest|nolink=1}} '06\n| 1907\n| <ref name=\"Universit